HEADWORD: Isotropy
<hw>I*sot"ro*py</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Physics)</fld>
<def>Uniformity of physical properties in all directions in a body;
absence of all kinds of polarity; specifically, equal elasticity in all
directions.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Isouric</ent>⟦br⟧
